    "description": "Hagihara Industries Inc., together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and sells plastic and industrial machinery products in Japan, Indonesia, Asia, and internationally. The company offers synthetic resin processing products, including flat yarns, monofilaments, sheets and sandbags, commercial printing and masking adhesive tapes, meltac cloths, base fabric for flexible container bag, artificial turf and carpet backing cloths, and barchips. It also provides engineering products, such as slitters, rewinders, yarn winders, plastic recycled pellet manufacturing equipment, extruder-related equipment, and GX line. The company exports its products. Its products are used in disaster prevention, architecture and civil engineering, industry and livestock farming, and household goods applications. Hagihara Industries Inc. was incorporated in 1962 and is headquartered in Kurashiki, Japan."
